quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  10,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  10,1,Alif Laaam Raa. yeh barri danai ki kitaab ki ayatain hain
  10,2,kiya logon ko taajjub howa ke hum ne un hi mein se aik mard ko hukum bheja ke logon ko dar suna do. aur imaan laane walon ko khushkhabri day do ke un ke perwar-digaar ke haan un ka sacha darja hai. ( aisay shakhs ki nisbat ) kafir kehte hain ke yeh Sarih jadugar hai
  10,3,"tumhara perwar-digaar to khuda hi hai jis ne aasman aur zameen chay din mein banaye phir arsh ( takhat Shahi ) par qaim howa wohi har aik ka intizam karta hai. koi ( is ke paas ) is ka azan haasil kiye baghair kisi ki sifarish nahi karsaktha, yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai to isi ki ibadat karo. bhala tum ghhor kyun nahi karte"
  10,4,isi ke paas tum sab ko lout kar jana hai. khuda ka wada sacha hai. wohi khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta hai. phir wohi is ko dobarah peda kere ga taakay imaan walon aur naik kaam karne walon ko insaaf ke sath badla day. aur jo kafir hain un ke liye peenay ko nihayat garam pani aur dard dainay wala azaab hoga kyun ke ( khuda se ) inkaar karte they
  10,5,wohi to hai jis ne Sooraj ko roshan aur chaand ko munhawar banaya aur chaand ki manzilain muqarrar kee taakay tum barson ka shumaar aur ( kamon ka ) hisaab maloom karo. yeh ( sab kuch ) khuda ne tadbeer se pedakiya hai. samajhney walon ke liye woh apni آیاتیں khol khol kar bayan farmata hai
  10,6,raat aur din ke ( aik dosray ke peechay ) anay jaane mein aur jo cheezein khuda ne aasman aur zameen mein peda ki hain ( sab mein ) darny walon ke liye nishanain hain
  10,7,jin logon ko hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi aur duniya ki zindagi se khush aur isi par mtymn ho baithy aur hamari nishanion se ghaafil ho rahay hain
  10,8,un ka thikana un ( aamaal ) ke sabab jo woh karte hain dozakh hai
  10,9,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un ko perwar-digaar un ke imaan ki wajah se ( aisay mehloon ki ) raah dukhaay ga ( ke ) un ke neechay Nemat ke baghoon mein nehrein beh rahi hon gi
  10,10,( jab woh ) un mein ( un nematon ko daikhon ge to be sakhta ) kahin ge subhan allah. aur aapas mein un ki dua salam alaikum hogi aur un ka aakhri qoul yeh ( hoga ) ke khuday-e rab alameen ki hamd ( aur is ka shukar ) hai
  10,11,aur agar khuda logon ki buraiee mein jaldi karta jis terhan woh talab kher mein jaldi karte hain. to un ki ( Umar ki ) meyaad poori hochuki hoti so jin logon ko hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi inhen hum chhorey rakhtay hain ke apni sar kashi mein behektey rahen
  10,12,aur jab ensaan ko takleef pahunchti hai to leyta aur betha aur khara ( har haal mein ) hamein pukaarta hai. phir jab hum is takleef ko is se daur kar dete hain to ( be lehaaz ho jata hai aur ) is terhan guzar jata hai goya kisi takleef pounchanay par hamein kabhi puraka hi nah tha. isi terhan hadd se nikal jaane walon ko un ke aamaal aaraasta karkay dukhaay gay hain
  10,13,aur tum se pehlay hum kayi amton ko jab unhon ne zulm ka rasta ikhtiyarkiya halaak kar chukay hain. aur un ke paas paighambar khuli nishanain le kar aeye magar woh aisay nah they ke imaan laatay. hum gunehgaar logon ko isi terhan badla diya karte hain
  10,14,phir hum ne un ke baad tum logon ko malik mein khalifa banaya taakay dekhen tum kaisay kaam karte ho
  10,15,aur jab un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to jin logon ko hum se milnay ki umeed nahi woh kehte hain ke ( ya to ) is ke siwa koi aur quran ( bana ) lao ya is ko badal do. keh do ke mujh ko ikhtiyar nahi hai ke usay apni taraf se badal do. mein to isi hukum ka tabay hon jo meri taraf aata hai. agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe barray ( sakht ) din ke azaab se khauf aata hai
  10,16,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke agar khuda chahta to ( nah to ) mein hi yeh ( kitaab ) tum ko parh kar sunataa aur nah wohi tumhe is se waaqif karta. mein is se pehlay tum mein aik Umar raha hon ( aur kabhi aik kalma bhi is terhan ka nahi kaha ) bhala tum samajte nahi
  10,17,to is se barh kar zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot aftara kere aur is ki ayaton ko jhutlaye. be shak gunehgaar Falah nahi payen ge
  10,18,aur yeh ( log ) khuda ke siwa aisi cheezon ki parastish karte hain jo nah un ka kuch bigaar hi sakti hain aur nah kuch bhala hi kar sakti hain aur kehte hain ke yeh khuda ke paas hamari sifarish karne walay hain. keh do kekiya tum khuda ko aisi cheez batatay ho jis ka wujood usay nah asmano mein maloom hota hai aur nah zameen mein. woh pak hai aur ( is ki shaan ) un ke shirk karne se bohat buland hai
  10,19,aur ( sab ) log ( pehlay ) aik hi aُmt ( yani aik hi millat par ) they. phir judda judda hogaye. aur agar aik baat jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se pehlay hochuki hai nah hoti to jin baton mein woh ikhtilaaf karte hain un mein faisla kar diya jata
  10,20,aur kehte hain ke is par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nazil nahi hui. keh do ke ghaib ( ka ilm ) to khuda ko hai so tum intzaar karo. mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
  10,21,aur jab hum logon ko takleef pounchanay ke baad ( apni ) rehmat ( se asayish ) ka maza chukhate hain to woh hamari ayaton mein heelay karne lagtay hain. keh do ke khuda bohat jald heela karne wala hai. aur jo heelay tum karte ho hamaray farishtay un ko likhte jatay hain
  10,22,wohi to hai jo tum ko jungle aur darya mein chalne phirnay aur sair karne ki tofeq deta hai. yahan taq ke jab tum kashtiyon mein ( sawaar ) hotay aur kashtiyan pakeeza howa ( ke naram naram jhonkon ) se sawaron ko le kar chalne lagti hain aur woh un se khush hotay hain to nagahan znatay ki howa chal padtee hai aur laharen har taraf se un par ( josh martii hui ) anay lagti hain aur woh khayaal karte hain ke ( ab to ) lehron mein ghar gay to is waqt khalis khuda hi ki ibadat karkay is se dua mangnay lagtay hain ke ( ae khuda ) agar to hum ko is se nijaat bakhshay to hum ( tairay ) bohat hi shukar guzaar hon
  10,23,lekin jab woh un ko nijaat day deta hai to malik mein na-haq shararat karne lagtay hain. logo! tumhari shararat ka wabaal tumhari hi jaanun par hoga tum duniya ki zindagi ke faiday uttha lau. phir tum ko hamaray paas lout kar aana hai. is waqt hum tum ko bitayen ge jo kuch tumkiya karte they
  10,24,duniya ki zindagi ki misaalmeinhہ ki si hai ke hum ne is ko aasman se barsaya. phir is ke sath sabza jisay aadmi aur janwar khatay hain mil kar nikla yahan taq ke zameen sabzay se khushnuma aur aaraasta hogayi aur zameen walon ne khayaalkiya ke woh is par poori dustarus rakhtay hain nagahan raat ko ya din ko hamara hukum ( azaab ) aap_hncha to hum ne is ko kaat ( kar aisa kar ) dala ke goya kal wahan kuch tha hi nahi. jo log ghhor karne walay hain. un ke liye hum ( apni qudrat ki ) nishanain isi terhan khol khol kar bayan karte hain
  10,25,aur khuda salamti ke ghar ki taraf bulaataa hai. aur jis ko chahta hai seedha rasta dekhata hai
  10,26,jin logon ne naiko kaari ki un ke liye bhalai hai aur ( mazeed bar-aan ) aur bhi aur un ke monhon par nah to siyahi chaaye gi aur nah ruswai. yahi janati hain ke is mein hamesha rahen ge
  10,27,aur jinhon ne buray kaam kiye to buraiee ka badla waisa hi hoga. aur un ke monhon par zillat chhaa jaye gi. aur koi un ko khuda se bachanay wala nah hoga. un ke monhon ( ki siyahi ka yeh aalam hoga ke un ) par goya andheri raat ke tukre udha diye gay hain. yahi dozakhi hain ke hamesha is mein rahen ge
  10,28,aur jis din hum un sab ko jama karen ge phir mushrikon se kahin ge ke tum aur tumahray shareek apni apni jagah thehray raho. to hum un mein tafarruqa daal den ge aur un ke shareek ( un se ) kahin ge ke tum hum ko nahi pooja karte they
  10,29,hamaray aur tumahray darmain khuda hi gawah kaafi hai. hum tumhari parastish se bilkul be khabar they
  10,30,wahan har shakhs ( apne aamaal ki ) jo is ne agay beje hon ge azmaish karle ga aur woh apne sachey maalik ki taraf lout’tay jayen ge aur jo kuch woh bohtan baandha karte they sab un se jata rahay ga
  10,31,( un se ) pucho ke tum ko aasman aur zameen mein rizaq kon deta hai ya ( tumahray ) kaanon aur aankhon ka maalik kon hai aur be jaan se jandaar kon peda karta hai aur duniya ke kamon ka intizam kon karta hai. jhat keh den ge ke khuda. to kaho ke phir tum ( khuda se ) drtay kyun nahi ?
  10,32,yahi khuda to tumhara perwar-digaar barhaq hai. aur haq baat ke zahir honay ke baad gumraahi ke siwa hai hikiya? to tum kahan phiray jatay ho
  10,33,isi terhan khuda ka irshad un na farmanoon ke haq mein saabit ho kar raha ke yeh imaan nahi layein ge
  10,34,( un se ) pucho ke bhala tumhare sharikon mein se koi aisa hai ke makhlooq ko abtdan peda kere ( aur ) phir is ko dobarah banaye? keh do ke khuda hi pehli baar peda karta hai phir wohi is ko dobarah peda kere ga to tum kahan uksay jarahay ho
  10,35,pucho ke bhala tumahray sharikon mein kon aisa hai ke haq ka rasta dukhaay. keh do ke khuda hi haq ka rasta dekhata hai. bhala jo haq ka rasta dukhaay woh is qabil hai ke uss ki pairwi ki jaye ya woh ke jab taq koi usay rasta nah betaye rasta nah paye. to tum kokiya howa hai kaisa insaaf karte ho ?
  10,36,aur un mein se aksar sirf zan ki pairwi karte hain. aur kuch shak nahi ke zan haq ke muqablay mein kuch bhi kaar amad nahi ho sakta. be shak khuda tumahray ( sab ) af-aal se waaqif hai
  10,37,aur yeh quran aisa nahi ke khuda ke siwa koi is ko apni taraf se bana laaye. haan ( haan yeh khuda ka kalaam hai ) jo ( kitaaben ) is se pehlay ( ki ) hain. un ki tasdeeq karta hai aur un hi kitabon ki ( is mein ) tafseel hai is mein kuch shak nahi ( ke ) yeh rab alameen ki taraf se ( nazil howa ) hai
  10,38,kiya yeh log kehte hain ke paighambar ne is ko apni taraf se bana liya hai keh do ke agar sachey ho to tum bhi is terhan ki aik sourat bana lao aur khuda ke siwa jin ko tum bulaa sakuu bulaa bhi lau
  10,39,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jis cheez ke ilm par yeh qaboo nahi paske is ko ( nadani se ) jhutla diya aur abhi is ki haqeeqat un par khuli hi nahi. isi terhan jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne takzieeb ki thi so dekh lau zaalmon ka injaam kaisa howa
  10,40,aur un mein se kuch to aisay hain ke is par imaan le atay hain aur kuch aisay hain ke imaan nahi laatay. aur tumahra perwar-digaar shariron se khoob waaqif hai
  10,41,aur agar yeh tumhari takzieeb karen to keh do ke mujh ko mere aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumahray aamaal ( ka ) tum mere amlon ka jawab da nahi ho aur mein tumahray amlon ka jawabdeh nahi hon
  10,42,aur un mein se baaz aisay hain ke tumhari taraf kaan lagatay hain tokiya tum behroon ko sunaaoo ge agarchay kuch bhi ( suntay ) samajte nah hon
  10,43,aur baaz aisay hain ke tumhari taraf dekhte hain. tokiya tum andhon ko rasta dikhao ge agarchay kuch bhi dekhte ( bhaltay ) nah hon
  10,44,khuda to logon par kuch zulm nahi karta lekin log hi apne aap par zulm karte hain
  10,45,aur jis din khuda un ko jama kere ga ( to woh duniya ki nisbat aisa khayaal karen ge ke ) goya ( wahan ) gharri bhar din se ziyada rahay hi nahi they ( aur ) aapas mein aik dosray ko shanakht bhi karen ge. jin logon ne khuda ke rubaroo haazir honay ko jhatlaya woh khasaray mein par gay aur raah yab nah hue
  10,46,aur agar hum koi azaab jis ka un logon se wada karte hain tumhari aankhon ke samnay ( nazil ) karen ya ( is waqt jab ) tumhari muddat hayaat poori kar dein to un ko hamaray hi paas lout kar aana hai phir jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain khuda is ko dekh raha hai
  10,47,aur har aik aُmt ki taraf se paighambar bheja gaya. jab un ka paighambar aata hai to unn mein insaaf ke sath faisla kar diya jata hai aur un par kuch zulm nahikiya jata
  10,48,aur yeh kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to ( jis azaab ka ) yeh wada ( hai woh aeye ga ) kab ?
  10,49,keh do ke mein apne nuqsaan aur faiday ka bhi kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. magar jo khuda chahay. har aik ummat ke liye ( mout ka ) aik waqt muqarrar hai. jab woh waqt ajata hai to aik gharri bhi der nahi kar saktay aur nah jaldi kar saktay hain
  10,50,keh do ke bhala dekho to agar is ka azaab tum par ( nagahan ) aajay raat ko ya din ko to phir gunehgaar kis baat ki jaldi karen ge
  10,51,kiya jab woh aa waqay hoga tab is par imaan lao ge ( is waqt kaha jaye ga ke ) aur ab ( imaan laaye? ) is ke liye to tum jaldi machaya karte they
  10,52,phir zalim logon se kaha jaye ga ke azaab daimi ka maza chako. ( ab ) tum inhen ( aamaal ) ka badla pao ge jo ( duniya mein ) karte rahay
  10,53,aur tum se daryaft karte hain ke aaya yeh sach hai. keh do haan khuda ki qasam sach hai aur tum ( bhaag kar khuda ko ) aajiz nahi krsko ge
  10,54,aur agar har aik nafarman shakhs ke paas roye zameen ki tamam cheezein hon to ( azaab se bachney ke ) badlay mein ( sab ) day daaley aur jab woh azaab ko dekhen ge to ( puchtain ge aur ) nedamat ko chupayen ge. aur un mein insaaf ke sath faisla kar diya jaye ga aur ( kisi terhan ka ) un par zulm nahi hoga
  10,55,sun rakho jo kuch asmano aur zamiinon mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai. aur yeh bhi sun rakho ke khuda ka wada sacha hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  10,56,wohi jaan bakhshta aur ( wohi ) mout deta hai aur tum log isi ki taraf lout kar jao ge
  10,57,logo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nasiyaat aur dilon ki bimarion ki Shifa . aur mominon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat aa pohanchi hai
  10,58,keh do ke ( yeh kitaab ) khuda ke fazl aur is ki meharbani se ( nazil hui hai ) to chahiye ke log is se khush hon. yeh is se kahin behtar hai jo woh jama karte hain
  10,59,kaho ke bhala dekho to khuda ne tumhare liye jo rizaq nazil farmaya to tum ne is mein se ( baaz ko ) haraam thehraya aur ( baaz ko ) halal ( un se ) puchokiya khuda ne tum ko is ka hukum diya hai ya tum khuda par iftira karte ho
  10,60,aur jo log khuda par iftira karte hain woh qayamat ke din ki nisbatkiya khayaal rakhtay hain? be shak khuda logon par meharban hai lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  10,61,aur tum jis haal mein hotay ho ya quran mein kuch parhte ho ya tum log koi ( aur ) kaam karte ho jab is mein masroof hotay ho hum tumahray samnay hotay hain aur tumahray perwar-digaar se zarra barabar bhi koi cheez posheeda nahi hai nah zameen mein nah aasman mein aur nah koi cheez is se choti hai ya barri magar kitaab roshan mein ( likhi hui ) hai
  10,62,sun rakho ke jo khuda ke dost hain un ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  10,63,( yani ) jo log imaan laaye aur parhaizgaar rahay
  10,64,un ke liye duniya ki zindagi mein bhi basharat hai aur akhirat mein bhi. khuda ki baatein badalti nahi. yahi to barri kamyabi hai
  10,65,aur ( ae paighambar ) un logon ki baton se aazurda nah hona ( kyunkay ) izzat sab khuda hi ki hai woh ( sab kuch ) santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  10,66,sun rakho ke jo makhlooq asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai sab khuda ke ( bande aur is ke mamlook ) hain. aur yeh jo khuda ke siwa ( apne banaye hue ) sharikon ko pkarte hain. woh ( kisi aur cheez ke ) peechay nahi chaltay. sirf zan ke peechay chaltay hain aur mehez atklin dora rahay hain
  10,67,wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai taakay is mein aaraam karo aur roz roshan banaya ( taakay is mein kaam karo ) jo log samaat rakhtay hain un ke liye un mein nishanain hain
  10,68,( baaz log ) kehte hain ke khuda ne beta bana liya hai. is ki zaat ( aulaad se ) pak hai ( aur ) woh be niaz hai. jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai woh sab isi ka hai ( ae iftira o pardazo ) tumahray paas is ( qoul baatil ) ki koi Daleel nahi hai. tum khuda ki nisbat aisi baat kyun kehte ho jo jantay nahi
  10,69,keh do jo log khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhtay hain Falah nahi payen ge
  10,70,( un ke liye jo ) faiday hain duniya mein ( hain ) phir un ko hamari hi taraf lout kar aana hai. is waqt hum un ko shadeed azaab ( ke mazay ) chkhayin ge kyunkay kufar ( ki baatein )kiya karte they
  10,71,aur un ko Nooh ka qissa parh kar suna do. jab unhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke ae qoum! agar tum ko mera tum mein rehna aur khuda ki ayaton se nasiyaat karna nagawaar ho to mein khuda par bharosa rakhta hon. tum apne sharikon ke sath mil kar aik kaam ( jo mere baray mein karna chaho ) muqarrar karlo aur woh tumhari tamam jamaat ( ko maloom hojaye aur kisi ) se posheeda nah rahay aur phir woh kaam mere haq mein kar guzro aur mujhe mohlat nah do
  10,72,aur agar tum ne munh phair liya to ( tum jantay ho ke ) mein ne tum se kuch muawza nahi manga. mera muawza to khuda ke zimmay hai. aur mujhe hukum howa hai ke mein farma -bardaron mein rahon
  10,73,lekin un logon ne un ki takzieeb ki to hum ne un ko aur jo log un ke sath kashti mein sawaar they sab ko ( tufaan se ) bacha liya aur inhen ( zameen mein ) khalifa banadiya aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya un ko ghark kar diya to dekh lau ke jo log dry gay they un kakiya injaam howa
  10,74,phir Nooh ke baad hum ne aur paighambar apni apni qoum ki taraf beje. to woh un ke paas khuli nishanain le kar aeye. magar woh log aisay nah they ke jis cheez ki pehlay takzieeb kar chukay they is par imaan le atay. isi terhan hum zayad-ti karne walon ke dilon par mohar laga dete hain
  10,75,phir un ke baad hum ne moose aur Haroon ko apni nishanain day kar firaon aur is ke sardaro ke paas bheja to unhon ne taqqaburkiya aur woh gunehgaar log they
  10,76,to jab un ke paas hamaray haan se haq aaya to kehnay lagey ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  10,77,moose ne kahakiya tum haq ke baray mein jab woh tumahray paas aaya yeh kehte ho ke yeh jaadoo hai. halaank jadugar Falah nahi panay ke
  10,78,woh bolaykiya tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke jis ( raah ) par hum apne baap dada ko paate rahay hain is se hum ko پھیردو. aur ( is ) malik mein tum dono ki hi sardari hojaye aur hum tum par imaan laane walay nahi hain
  10,79,aur firaon ne hukum diya ke sab kaamil fungado garon ko hamaray paas le aao
  10,80,jab jadugar aeye to moose ne un se kaha tum ko jo daalna hai daalo
  10,81,jab unhon ne ( apni rassiyon aur lathyon ko ) dala to moose ne kaha ke jo cheezein tum ( bana kar ) laaye ho jaadoo hai khuda is ko bhi naist vnabod kardey ga. khuda shariron ke kaam sanvara nahi karta
  10,82,aur khuda apne hukum se sach ko sach hi kardey ga agarchay gunehgaar bura hi manen
  10,83,to moose par koi imaan nah laya. magar is ki qoum mein se chand larke ( aur woh bhi ) firaon aur is ke ahal darbaar se drtay drtay ke kahin woh un ko aafat mein nah phansa day. aur firaon mulk mein mutaqabbir o mutaghalib aur ( kibar o kufr ) mein hadd se barha howa tha
  10,84,aur moose ne kaha ke bhaio! agar tum khuda par imaan laaye ho to agar ( dil se ) farmanbardar ho to isi par bharosa rakho
  10,85,to woh bolay ke hum khuda hi par bharosa rakhtay hain. ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko zalim logon ke haath se azmaish mein nah daal
  10,86,aur apni rehmat se qoum kufar se nijaat bakhash
  10,87,aur hum ne moose aur is ke bhai ki taraf wahi bhaije ke apne logon ke liye misar mein ghar banaao aur apne gharon ko qibla ( yani masjiden ) thehrao aur namaz parho. aur mominon ko khushkhabri suna do
  10,88,aur moose ne kaha ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne firaon aur is ke sardaro ko duniya ki zindagi mein ( bohat sa ) sazu barg aur maal vzr day rakha hai. ae perwar-digaar un ka maal yeh hai ke tairay raste se gumraah kar dein. ae perwar-digaar un ke maal ko barbaad kardey aur un ke dilon ko sakht kardey ke imaan nah layein jab taq azaab alim nah dekh len
  10,89,khuda ne farmaya ke tumhari dua qubool karli gayi to tum saabit qadam rehna aur be aqlon ke raste nah chalna
  10,90,aur hum ne bani Israel ko darya se paar kardiya to firaon aur is ke lashkar ne sar kashi aur ta-adi se un ka taqubkiya. yahan taq ke jab is ko ghark ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha to kehnay laga ke mein imaan laya ke jis ( khuda ) par bani Israel imaan laaye hain is ke siwa koi mabood nahi aur mein farmabardaron mein hon
  10,91,( jawab mila ke ) ab ( imaan lata hai ) halaank to pehlay nafarmani karta raha aur mufsid bana raha
  10,92,to aaj hum tairay badan ko ( darya se ) nikaal len ge taakay to pichlon ke liye Ibrat ho. aur bohat se log hamari nishanion se be khabar hain
  10,93,aur hum ne bani Israel ko rehne ko umdah jagah di aur khanay ko pakeeza cheezein ataa kee lekin woh bawajood ilm honay ke ikhtilaaf karte rahay. be shak jin baton mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain tumhara perwar-digaar qayamat ke din un mein un baton ka faisla kardey ga
  10,94,agar tum ko is ( kitaab ke ) baray mein jo hum ne tum par nazil ki hai kuch shak ho to jo log tum se pehlay ki ( utreen hui ) kitaaben parhte hain un se pooch lau. tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas haq aachuka hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona
  10,95,aur nah un logon mein hona jo khuda ki ayaton ki takzieeb karte hain nahi to nuqsaan uthao ge
  10,96,jin logon ke baray mein khuda ka hukum ( azaab ) qarar pachka hai woh imaan nahi laane ke
  10,97,jab taq ke azaab alim nah dekh len khuwa un ke paas har ( terhan ki ) nishani aajay
  10,98,to koi bastii aisi kyun nah hui ke imaan latayen to is ka imaan usay naffa deta haan Younis ki qoum. jab imaan layi to hum ne duniya ki zindagi mein un se zillat ka azaab daur kardiya aur aik muddat taq ( fawaid dunyawi se ) un ko behra mand rakha
  10,99,aur agar tumhara perwar-digaar chahta to jitne log zameen par hain sab ke sab imaan le atay. tokiya tum logon par zabardasti karna chahtay ho ke woh momin ho jaien
  10,100,halaank kisi shakhs ko qudrat nahi hai ke khuda ke hukum ke baghair imaan laaye. aur jo log be aqal hain un par woh ( kufar o zillat ki ) najasat dalta hai
  10,101,( un kufar se ) kaho dekho to zameen aur asmano meinkiya kuch hai. magar jo log imaan nahi rakhtay un ki nishanain aur draway kuch kaam nahi atay
  10,102,so jaisay ( buray ) din un se pehlay logon par guzar chuke hain isi terhan ke ( dinon ke ) yeh munhtazir hain. keh do ke tum bhi intzaar karo. mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
  10,103,aur hum apne payghambaroon ko aur mominon ko nijaat dete rahay hain. isi terhan hamara zimma hai ke musalmanoon ko nijaat den
  10,104,( ae paighambar ) keh do ke logo agar tum ko mere deen mein kisi terhan ka shak ho to ( sun rakho ke ) jin logon ki tum khuda ke siwa ibadat karte ho mein un ki ibadat nahi karta. balkay mein khuda ki ibadat karta hon jo tumhari roohein qabz karleta hai aur mujh ko yahi hukum howa hai ke imaan laane walon mein hon
  10,105,aur yeh ke ( ae Mohammad sab se ) yaksu ho kar deen ( islam ) ki pairwi kiye jao. aur mushrikon mein hargiz nah hona
  10,106,aur khuda ko chore kar aisi cheez ko nah pukarna jo nah tumhara kuch bhala kar sakay aur nah kuch bigaar sakay. agar aisa karo ge to zaalmon mein hojao ge
  10,107,aur agar khuda tum ko koi takleef pohnchaye to is ke siwa is ka koi daur karne wala nahi aur agar tum se bhalai karni chahay to is ke fazl ko koi roknay wala nahi. woh apne bundon mein se jisay chahta hai faida pohanchata hai aur woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  10,108,keh do ke logo tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan se tumahray paas haq aachuka hai to jo koi hadaayat haasil karta hai to hadaayat se apne hi haq mein bhalai karta hai. aur jo gumraahi ikhtiyar karta hai to gumraahi se apna hi nuqsaan karta hai. aur mein tumhara wakeel nahi hon
  10,109,aur ( ae paighambar ) tum ko jo hukum bheja jata hai is ki pairwi kiye jao aur ( tklifon par ) sabr karo yahan taq ke khuda faisla kardey. aur woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
